[[File:Ore_mine_256.png|right]]The '''Iron Mine''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It produces iron. Any bordering ore deposits, [[Cottage]]s and a maximum of one [[Foundry]] will increase productivity.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 4

